    <summary>This extension replaces the image gallery with the cloudZoom widget.</summary>
    <description>For this extension, the regular image gallery of Magento will be replaced by the cloudZoom widget. This enables customers to hover over product images and bring up a zoom view, instead of using controls.

Features:

Smooth zoom movement.
Define the dimensions of the zoom window.
Define the position of the zoom window.
Z/Y pixel spaces for the zoom window.
Show or Hide the title on top of the zoom window. Also, define the opacity.
Define lens opacity.
Dimensions of the main image.
Soft focus and inner zoom features.
Overlay color and opacity on hover.
To Configure it you can navigate to "System &gt; Configuration &gt; Catalog &gt; Moo Product Gallery "CloudZoom"</description>
